ery useful gift indeed, for it was with this bow that Legolas shot down the descending [[Fell beasts|Fell beast]] from the sky, near the rapids of [[Sarn Gebir]].<ref>{{FR|II9}}, p. 387</ref>\n\n{{weapons}}\n{{Giftsofgaladriel}}\n{{references}}\n\n[[Category:Bows]]\n[[Category:Gifts of Galadriel]]"}}}